{"tid":577727,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"史尼達談當年為何拒利物浦：我想奪更多冠軍","createTime":"2018-03-02T04:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T07:12:35.000Z","uid":147522,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c36aed0e2cf07f32a6a8b1bab35aa5edfb318dd6","tid":577727,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:14:39.000Z","msg":"在2013年的時候，前荷蘭國腳史尼達曾有機會加盟利物浦，但是他最終卻選擇轉會去了加拉塔沙雷，史尼達近日在接受媒體採訪時表示，他認為去加拉塔沙雷能夠拿到更多冠軍，所以拒絕了利物浦。<br />\n　　<br />\n「當時有許多球會都想知道我會在什麼時候離開國米，利物浦就是其中之一。然而我最終選擇了加拉塔沙雷，這讓許多人大吃一驚。」史尼達對記者說道。<br />\n　　<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「為什麼不去利物浦？因為我是一個贏家。我只會為了冠軍與榮譽而戰，所以我最終選擇了加拉塔沙雷，因為我覺得與利物浦相比起來，我能夠在土超獲得更多冠軍，我認為我做出了正確的選擇。」<br />\n　　</span><br />\n「我在土耳其度過了幾年非常美好的時光。」史尼達一共為加拉塔沙雷效力了4年半的時間，他幫助球隊拿到了2個土超聯賽的冠軍以及3個土耳其國內盃賽的冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d7bb7de7a6d65fd50e317a9b24503d0ac96fa7","tid":577727,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"真曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f7fbb173ca62251fd30d92e4f597acc0ecb62e","tid":577727,"uid":23116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55455bf400941c2f6e11dde5a8773dcbfa81eea1","tid":577727,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a12ed7f496acc5e774c1b9baa3609229db1d661","tid":577727,"u